@apiKey = T6QI93RPV43NN0KF
@floatAssetsUrl = https://www.steamwebapi.com/steam/api/float/assets
@youpinPricesUrl = https://www.steamwebapi.com/market/youpin/prices
@itemsUrl = https://www.steamwebapi.com/steam/api/items
@itemUrl = https://www.steamwebapi.com/steam/api/item
@itemsPreviewUrl = https://www.steamwebapi.com/steam/api/items/preview
@backendUrl = http://localhost:3001/api

### YouPin — AK-47 | Redline (Field-Tested)
GET {{floatAssetsUrl}}?key={{apiKey}}&appid=730&market_hash_name=AK-47%20%7C%20Redline%20%28Field-Tested%29&source=youpin
Accept: application/json

