### YouPin — Sticker | Reason Gaming | Katowice 2014
GET {{floatAssetsUrl}}?key={{apiKey}}&appid=730&market_hash_name=Sticker%20%7C%20Reason%20Gaming%20%7C%20Katowice%202014&source=youpin
