### Catálogo YouPin — sync masivo (igual que backend: newest, limit=50)
GET {{floatAssetsUrl}}?key={{apiKey}}&appid=730&source=youpin&only_market_id=1&with_items=1&limit=50&offset=0&sort=newest
Accept: application/json

### On-demand por skin — mejor float primero (igual que modal)
GET {{floatAssetsUrl}}?key={{apiKey}}&appid=730&source=youpin&only_market_id=1&with_items=1&market_hash_name=AK-47%20%7C%20Redline%20%28Field-Tested%29&limit=12&offset=0&sort=lowest_float
Accept: application/json

###
### Market Prices — YouPin (precios bots / GET /market/youpin/prices)
###

### YouPin prices — catálogo completo (USD)
GET {{youpinPricesUrl}}?key={{apiKey}}&currency=USD
Accept: application/json

### YouPin prices — AK-47 | Redline (Field-Tested)
GET {{youpinPricesUrl}}?key={{apiKey}}&currency=USD&market_hash_name=AK-47%20%7C%20Redline%20%28Field-Tested%29
Accept: application/json

### YouPin prices — ★ Butterfly Knife | Doppler (Minimal Wear) (puede incluir variants)
GET {{youpinPricesUrl}}?key={{apiKey}}&currency=USD&market_hash_name=%E2%98%85%20Butterfly%20Knife%20%7C%20Doppler%20%28Minimal%20Wear%29
Accept: application/json

### YouPin prices — ★ M9 Bayonet | Doppler (Factory New) | Black Pearl
GET {{youpinPricesUrl}}?key={{apiKey}}&currency=USD&market_hash_name=%E2%98%85%20M9%20Bayonet%20%7C%20Doppler%20%28Factory%20New%29%20%7C%20Black%20Pearl
Accept: application/json

### YouPin prices — AWP | Dragon Lore (Factory New)
GET {{youpinPricesUrl}}?key={{apiKey}}&currency=USD&market_hash_name=AWP%20%7C%20Dragon%20Lore%20%28Factory%20New%29
Accept: application/json

###
### Items API — pruebas precios YouPin con fases Doppler
###

### Items API — buscar M9 Bayonet Doppler en mercado YouPin
GET {{itemsUrl}}?key={{apiKey}}&game=cs2&search=M9%20Bayonet%20Doppler&item_group=knife&wear=fn&markets=youpin&currency=USD&select=markethashname,pricereal,pricemix,pricelatest,image&production=1
Accept: application/json

### Items API — catálogo global CS2 con precios YouPin/USD (misma base del JSON local)
GET {{itemsUrl}}?key={{apiKey}}&game=cs2&page=1&max=50000&markets=youpin&currency=USD&production=1&select=markethashname,marketname,normalizedname,pricereal,pricemix,pricelatest,prices,paintindex,variants,itemgroup,itemname,itemtype,wear,isstattrak,issouvenir,image
Accept: application/json

### Item API — detalle base con groups/variants y precios YouPin
GET {{itemUrl}}?key={{apiKey}}&market_hash_name=%E2%98%85%20M9%20Bayonet%20%7C%20Doppler%20%28Factory%20New%29&currency=USD&with_groups=true&markets=youpin&production=1
Accept: application/json

### Item API — AK-47 | Redline (Field-Tested) precio YouPin USD
GET {{itemUrl}}?key={{apiKey}}&market_hash_name=AK-47%20%7C%20Redline%20%28Field-Tested%29&currency=USD&with_groups=true&markets=youpin&production=1
Accept: application/json

### Item API — StatTrak™ AK-47 | Redline (Field-Tested) precio YouPin USD
GET {{itemUrl}}?key={{apiKey}}&market_hash_name=StatTrak%E2%84%A2%20AK-47%20%7C%20Redline%20%28Field-Tested%29&currency=USD&with_groups=true&markets=youpin&production=1
Accept: application/json

### Item API — Souvenir AK-47 | Safari Mesh (Field-Tested) precio YouPin USD
GET {{itemUrl}}?key={{apiKey}}&market_hash_name=Souvenir%20AK-47%20%7C%20Safari%20Mesh%20%28Field-Tested%29&currency=USD&with_groups=true&markets=youpin&production=1
Accept: application/json

### Items Preview — fases disponibles para M9 Bayonet Doppler (sin precios)
GET {{itemsPreviewUrl}}?key={{apiKey}}&search=M9%20Bayonet%20Doppler&only_phases=true&grouped=true&pretty=1
Accept: application/json

###
### Backend — estado del catálogo local de precios
GET {{backendUrl}}/store/prices/catalog/status
Accept: application/json

### Backend — refrescar catálogo local de precios desde /steam/api/items
POST {{backendUrl}}/store/prices/catalog/refresh
Accept: application/json
